   -M_1  \leq f'(x) = f'(x_0) + f''(\xi)(x-x_0) \leq M_1 + M_2(x-x_0) 
x - x_0 =  4 M_0 - \dfrac{2M_1}{M_2} - M_1 ^2 
x, x_0 \in D
